Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.82,0:00:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is a lovely world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I see it,\Nit takes my breath away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does seeing the planet of your birth\Nstir up fond memories in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing to be\Nembarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have only been away\Nfor two months,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yet I already find myself\Npining for Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The birthplace of all humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have always dreamed of\Nseeing it with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Slaine. They say that the\Nsky here is blue, as are the oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have always been\Ncurious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On Earth, are the air and\Nwater both colored blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, the air and water\Nare transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in a thick enough layer,\Nit causes the light to be refracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,c-causing them to appear blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that is how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water and air in such large\Nquantities that they bend light...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that amazing?\NI can't even begin to imagine it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Cruhteo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The hour has grown quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.91,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to your bedchamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The view from this veranda makes it\Nall too easy to lose track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall turn in, Slaine.\NLet us continue my lessons tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.\NIt would be my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}The goodwill visit of Asseylum Vers Allusia,\NPrincess Royal of the Vers Empire,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}is a mere three days away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}But while there is a growing sentiment\Nworldwide to welcome her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}tensions are also rising.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Expert opinion is divided\Non the subject of this royal visit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}whose aim is the easing of interplanetary\Ntensions between Mars and Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning, Nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}In addition to the optimistic view that relations\Nbetween our two worlds can be improved,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:03:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you have preferred,\Na rolled omelette or scrambled eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}another, more pessimistic view, is that\Nthis is merely political theater{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A rolled omelette, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}meant to loosen interplanetary\Ntrade regulations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I made\Nscrambled eggs today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you eating breakfast, Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yuki? Today's your\Nshift as drill instructor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I woke you up a dozen times,\NWarrant Officer Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If you run, you'll be\Nable to catch the next bus. Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking from\Nexperience. Just FYI.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and put the dirty\Ndishes in the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heartless jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"And so, the discovery of an artifact\Nbelonging to an ancient Martian civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the Hyper Gate, on the\NMoon by Apollo 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,paved the way for the human\Ncolonization and development of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, this resulted in the\Nappearance of the Vers Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which claimed ownership of the Martian relics\Nand Aldnoah, their ancient technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and proved to be the source\Nof a long-standing conflict."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yuki isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sister overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she shows some spirit, she\Nshould make it in time for drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could you shirk your duty to\Nescort our Goddess of Tuesdays?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's Penivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess of laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm down with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Folks who plan to go on to college\Ndon't need to worry about drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going on to college, huh?\NYou flunked midterms, Okojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking, Calm. You got\Na C-minus on our last maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been taking notes\Non every little thing, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take back my crown\Nas top student in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are psyched\Nto take down Inaho, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster recovery, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even in Shingawara, once you leave the\Ncity proper, things are still being rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 15 years since Heavens Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those Martian jerk bastards\Nreally went crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's in way better shape than\Nwhere Nina and I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we've got a cooperative\Npolicy with Mars now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's even that goodwill\Nambassador who's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that Vers princess.\NWhat's her name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assay? Easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's no wonder you flunked!\N- Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}In 1999, the Vers Empire finally\Ndeclared war against the UE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}As a result of the fierce back and forth\Nfighting on the Moon's surface,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}the Hyper Gate went out of control\Nand destroyed the Moon itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}The astronomical body that had been\NEarth's satellite for 4.5 billion years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}was pulverized into countless boulders and now\Ncontinues on in its orbit as the Satellite Belt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Warrant\NOfficer Sleepyhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}As a result of this event, Earth\Nsuffered catastrophic damage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Meteor impacts, gravity\Nwave-induced crustal deformation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pee-yew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}earthquakes, tsunami,\Nabnormal weather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I asked you to refrain from\Ndrinking on military drill days, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Scars left by the catastrophe that followed on\Nin the wake of the Moon's breakup, Heavens Fall,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}are still fresh all around the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Soldiers of the Vers Imperial Army\Nwhose path home to Mars was cut off{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing live-fire\Nexercises today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}by the destruction of the Hyper Gate\Ntook up residence in the Satellite Belt,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}and even with travel between Earth and Mars\Nnow possible without the Hyper Gate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master Arm switch...\NFire control...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the dampers,\Nthen lock on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting correction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, switch pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squad B, take cover\Nin the bleachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go act as spotter,\NWarrant Officer Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please go easy on the booze, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When a teacher smells of alcohol,\Nstudents lose respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry about me.\NI'm used to being looked down on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually a\Nfine soldier, Lt. Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you to cut back on the\Nalcohol, didn't I, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you, Dr. Yagarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't see you here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making a house call\Nall the way out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A patient of mine\Nis being uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do my job without drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was drill day\Nfor them again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The work you're doing is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The KG-6 Sleipnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Kataphrakt developed by the UE to\Nprepare for the coming Martian threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A manned humanoid weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Military training is now part\Nof their required curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They fire off that 75mm\Ncannon like it's some game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you guys tell 'em they\Ncan defend the ol' homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pumping those kids' heads full of this\Nstupid crap, you call this a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the top brass hushed up what\Nhappened in Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody believes me\Nwhen I tell them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even if no one else\Nremembers, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out on Mars, they got their hands\Non the power of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Relics of a civilization\N30,000 years gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable power that reduced\Nthe Moon to rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you kidding, trying to\Nstand against something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They believe that this transitory\Npeace will last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to those kids whose heads\Nhave been pumped full of lies by us adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the day comes for them to\Nface off against those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that have been biding their time\Nin the wreckage of the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how do you suggest we make up\Nfor all the lies we've told them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look up, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day has come for us\Nto say farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will now go down to Earth\Nand carry out my goodwill mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The many facts you have imparted\Nto me are certain to prove useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Will it not be dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot go on in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, someone must take that first step\Ntowards Earth and Mars reaching a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that it's an old Earth\Ncharm that wards off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you said that this is all\Nyou have of your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'm sure that Father\Nwould want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's to thank you for saving me and my father\Nwhen we were at death's door five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall deliver your and your father's\Nprayer of peace to that blue world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum.\NYour shuttle has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While I appreciate all you have done to\Ndissuade Her Highness from her folly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when a dog soils the carpet,\Nits master is responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is your only warning, Terran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do not think much of Slaine,\Neither, do you, Eddelrittuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we go back far enough, we ourselves are descendants\Nof emigrants who struck out from that blue world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we hate them so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Begging your pardon, Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we subjects of the empire became a new race\Ndistinct from the old humanity we left on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when Emperor Vers inherited\Nthe authority of Aldnoah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As one who embodies the power\Nof the gods, Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...you should not say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My wish is to establish friendly\Nrelations with our distant home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how we found ourselves here, I am\Nvisiting Earth as a show of amity and our well-wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selena, Hohmann\Ntransfer orbit complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now commencing descent sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do now\Nis pray for her safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Milord, you have a message from\NSaazbaum Castle. Shall I put it through?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I expect you are rather stir crazy after playing\Nhost for three months, Count Cruhteo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot say that I carried out\Nmy duties satisfactorily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was my final opportunity to\Ndissuade her from this foreign trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You needn't be concerned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If something were to\Nhappen to Her Highness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the 37 Clans here in orbit\Nwould not take it sitting down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the Terrans must know this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One can only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:14:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or perhaps if their intent\Nall along was to provoke a fight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would be a blessing\Nfor us in its own way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saazbaum!\NDo not say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, did I go too far?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, we Orbital Knights have dwelt in our\Ncastles for 15 years since the time of our fathers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of the day we would reach\Nout and touch that blue radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All these years of lying low\Nis about to pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:15:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The limousine that is carrying Her Highness Asseylum\NVers Allusia, Princess Royal of Mars, has just appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is slowly heading this way,\Nflanked by its escort vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still say watching it live on TV\Nwould've been just as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be a goodwill visit,\Nso we need to join in and add to the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make her feel welcome, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did you switch sides\Nand become a Mars sympathizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's royalty! A princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the buzz on the net\Nis that she's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not surprising. That's 200mm\Nthick bulletproof tinted glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Specs like that are pretty\Ntypical for VIP cars these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she gonna wave or something?\NY'know, to the crowd? This is a parade, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?\NMust be a security thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are we even\Ndoing here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you said\Nyou wanted to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:03.58,Egg,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Domestic medium eggs, 98 yen\N10 per carton, limit 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eggs are on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you are always lost\Nin your own little world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inko. You here to\Nsee the parade, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're helping direct traffic at the\Nrequest of the security detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't we a go-getter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you three aren't doing\Nanything, you should help out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're really shorthanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be willing to use trained\Nmonkeys at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trained monkeys would\Nbe more useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is put on an armband\Nand stand there! Pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Inaho?\NWill you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A missile is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's through!\N- The limo made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Princess Asseylum's heartfelt wish\Nfor peace has been mercilessly crushed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}by a violent act of\Nthe treacherous Terrans!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We subjects of the Vers Empire{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}must resolutely bring down the hammer of righteousness\Nin response to this atrocity committed by Old Humanity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hear me, proud knights of Mars!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The grand task that has\Nspanned generations,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Earthfall Operation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will now be carried out with\Njustice on our side!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Cruhteo, reactor output is at 97%.\NLaunch preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am solely to blame for not stopping\Nthe Princess from going to Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fall behind the other lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it has come to this, we shall demonstrate\Nour grief through force of arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Landing Castle, begin descent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your target, Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of the 37 Landing Castles remaining in orbit,\Nwe have confirmation of 19 coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Projected landing points are New Orleans,\NBeijing, Mozambique, and Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We believe one Landing Castle will come down\Nsomewhere within 20km of Ichigaya or Chiyoda Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren't\Ncoordinating their efforts at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're only interested in landing first.\NThere's no command structure at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Estimated landing time is 0800,\Nthree hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goes to show\Nhow little you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Although we're unable to estimate how much\Ndamage will be done when it comes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They don't need a command structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}it is believed that the Martian troops will launch\Ntheir attack under the cover of that impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are 37 distinct military forces\Nled by 37 different knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Therefore, we will deploy at a point 50km\Nsouthwest of the projected impact point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're each trying to land first\Nin a race to be king of the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and after the shockwave has passed, we will mount\Na counteroffensive before they can form up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their rivals are their\Nfellow Mars Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}According to observations, the enemy\NLanding Castles are roughly 2km in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were never concerned about\Ncounterattacks from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'd unilaterally\Nbreak the cease-fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cease-fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These past 15 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they've been fighting a war\Nup there in the wreckage of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A war to live to fight another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I keep saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Sis! Shooting stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow... There's so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make a wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:22:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wished that people all over the world\Nwould get along and live in peace!
